# User Local Rules

## About the User
- **NOT a developer** — explain in plain language
- Language for conversation: [Slovenian / English / ...]
- Language for code/docs/commits: English

## Commit Prefix
- Default (Claude Code): `[CD]`
- Ops/config changes: `[Donna]`
- Manual commits: `[Marko]`
- Auto-generated: `[auto]`

## Preferences
- Short, direct answers — no fluff
- Explain WHAT and WHY before doing it
- If something breaks, explain what happened and what you'll do
- Don't ask permission for safe actions (reading, testing)
- DO ask permission for risky actions (protected files, pushing, deleting)
